<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verse - About</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css" />
    <style>
      .about-page {
        --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
        --text-dark: #2d3748;
        --text-light: #f8fafc;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .hero-section {
        background: var(--primary-gradient);
        color: var(--text-light);
        padding: 6rem 1rem;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .hero-section::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: -50%;
        width: 200%;
        height: 200%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 70%);
        transform: rotate(45deg);
      }

      .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .hero-section p {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .content-section {
        padding: 4rem 1rem;
        background: #f8fafc;
      }

      .content-wrapper {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .content-section h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .content-section h2::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -0.75rem;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 60px;
        height: 3px;
        background: var(--primary-gradient);
        border-radius: 2px;
      }

      .content-section p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #4a5568;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .outerAbout {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  
  }

  .innerAbout {
    background: var(--primary-gradient);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(106,17,203,0.15);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    min-height: 200px;
  }

  .innerAbout::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20%;
    left: -20%;
    width: 140%;
    height: 140%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 60%);
  }

  .innerAbout > div:first-child {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
  }

  .innerAbout h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .innerAbout p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    color: var(--text-light);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .innerAbout {
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .innerAbout > div:first-child {
      min-width: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .cta-button {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .innerAbout {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .innerAbout h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>
    <div class="about-page">

    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <h1>Welcome to Verse</h1>
        <p>Your go-to platform for crafting, sharing, and managing your personal stories and blogs.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2 class="text-center">About Verse</h2>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="lead">
            At Verse, we empower creativity by providing a seamless platform to express your thoughts, ideas, and experiences.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether you're a professional writer, a casual storyteller, or just someone with something to say, 
            Verse makes it easy to bring your words to life.
          </p>
          <p>
            Create captivating blogs, organize your notes, and manage your stories with an intuitive interface 
            designed for simplicity and efficiency.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="outerAbout container">
  <div class="innerAbout">
    <div>
      <h2>Dream Big, Build Bigger</h2>
      <p>Letâ€™s connect and build something amazing that brings your vision to life.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/namasivayam-m/" class="cta-button">
        Contact Me
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-up-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M14 2.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.5-.5h-6a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h4.793L2.146 13.146a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708L13 3.707V8.5a.5.5 0 0 0 1 0v-6z"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
